                            <comment id="13201571" author="brandon.williams" created="Mon, 6 Feb 2012 20:49:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately, there&apos;s nothing we can do about pig catching errors and rethrowing the &quot;org.apache.pig.impl.logicalLayer.FrontendException: ERROR 2042: Error in new logical plan. Try -Dpig.usenewlogicalplan=false.&quot; message, but we can at least throw a helpful error into the log instead of an NPE.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
